data.title: IT Support Specialist - Ascend Analytics
data.meta_description: Only matches tailored to your preferences. Only the most exciting, innovative and fast-moving companies.
data.text: Whilst many analytics companies in its industry made the switch to energy and renewable analytics in the last decade, Ascend Analytics has been at it for 20+ years, giving them the edge over the competition. The software and consulting company has been providing solutions for the power transition to renewables since 2002, and is a seasoned partner to more than 100 energy companies in North America and Europe.
